HEADWORD: Homosystemic
<hw>Ho`mo*sys*tem"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Homo-</ets> + <ets>systemic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld>
<def>Developing, in the case of multicellular organisms, from the same
embryonic systems into which the secondary unit (gastrula or plant
enbryo) differentiates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Homotaxia</ent>⟦br⟧
